data.description: Country living at its finest! This four bedroom with large bonus room and three and a half bath home is situated on a sprawling 2.6-acre lot within the highly sought-after Rehoboth school district. Boasting a spacious open concept design, this home offers a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite countertops, beautiful cabinet lights with ample cabinetry, and a convenient center island. Large master with a large walk-in closet also features a spa like bathroom with a Jacuzzi tub and a huge walk-in shower with dual shower heads. Two of the other bedrooms in addition to the master have their own private bath rooms. Another great feature is the large 24 x 36 powered workshop, which offers endless possibilities. Whether you're a hobbyist, need additional storage space, or dream of having your own home office or gym, this workshop is sure to exceed your expectations. The 2.6-acre lot provides ample room for outdoor activities and the opportunity to create your own private oasis.
